title: Eid Gift Box
description: Experience the joy of giving with this unique Eid Gift Box. Showcasing exquisite Islamic geometric designs on its four interchangeable sides, this box can be customized to your taste. Choose a contrasting color to make the patterns pop. The box and lid are designed to be printed in a spiralized mode for a smooth finish and efficient material usage. Depending on how sturdy you want it, set your bottom layers to 3 or 4 for the box and 0 for the lid. Print the panels with normal settings for the best results. Check out the video to see it in action!
